Class DataProviderUtility.GoogleSheet

java.lang.Object
functional.utilities.DataProviderUtility.GoogleSheet
Enclosing class:
DataProviderUtility
protected static class DataProviderUtility.GoogleSheet extends Object
Nested static class for interacting with Google Sheets. Provides functionalities to manipulate and retrieve data from Google Sheets.
